  "prompt": "What is best institute in Hyderabad for group 2 exams?",
  "response": "There are several reputed coaching institutes in Hyderabad that specialize in preparing students for Group 2 exams, such as those conducted by the Telangana Public Service Commission (TSPSC). Some of the well-known institutes include:\n\n1. **RC Reddy IAS Study Circle**: This institute is renowned for its experienced faculty and comprehensive study materials.\n   \n2. **Analog IAS Institute**: They offer specialized coaching for state public service exams and have a good track record.\n   \n3. **La Excellence IAS Academy**: Known for their personalized coaching and results-driven approach.\n   \n4. **Brain Tree Institute**: Offers well-structured courses and has experienced faculty members.\n   \n5. **Telangana Study Circle**: Provides free coaching for eligible candidates and focuses on state-level exams.\n   \nEach of these institutes has its strengths, so the \"best\" one may vary depending on individual needs, budget, and learning preferences. It's a good idea to visit these institutes, if possible, to understand their teaching methodologies and speak with current or former students before making a decision.",
